  <name>GlowBerry</name>
  <summary>Enhanced background service with live shader support</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      GlowBerry is an enhanced background/wallpaper service with live shader wallpaper support,
      allowing animated GPU-rendered backgrounds using WGSL shaders.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Live GPU-rendered shader wallpapers</li>
      <li>Static image wallpapers (JPEG, PNG, WebP, JPEG XL)</li>
      <li>Solid color and gradient backgrounds</li>
      <li>Slideshow rotation</li>
      <li>Per-output configuration</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
